    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with all major mechanical systems in solid working order. While there are some minor cosmetic signs of use consistent with its age, the interior is clean and the electronics are fully functional. You can expect a dependable driving experience with no immediate repairs necessary.",
