    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it was manufactured. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless with a deep, showroom shine, free of any scratches, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in perfect state, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and showing no signs of creasing or wear. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions perfectly, and the engine bay is spotlessly clean. This is a collector-quality example that has been meticulously garage-kept and maintained to the highest possible standards.",
