    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an incredible deal and a project to make your own? This car is the perfect canvas for someone who loves to tinker and bring a vehicle back to life! While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it's a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity to get behind the wheel of a car with plenty of potential left to give.",
